// rules for responding to surface and object events
// ==================================================

RULE 1 - "If an object is red then it is interesting"
    if:   hq-1 -lex-  red
               -hq--> obj-1
         ako-1 -lex-  object
               -ako-> obj-1
  then:   hq-2 -lex-  interesting
               -hq--> obj-1

